      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. TOOLITTLETOOLATE was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start when he settled well back over 1006m at this track, beaten 3 lengths into sixth. Best figures measure up nicely. Sure to run well. 6. STAN FROM MALIBU finished third at this track two runs back but was less effective last time over 1006m at Turf Paradise Turf (Turf), finishing 8 lengths back in seventh. Finds a nice race and can bounce back. 7. SARGE'S SERMON turned things around last start and landed the prize by a nose over 1609m at this track (Dirt). Meeting a deeper field this time but he deserves plenty of thought. 2. BAD SNEAKERS was returning from a break last time out and proved too classy, scoring by 1.3 lengths over 1308m at this track (Dirt). Will be better for that latest run and is worth following up.\",\"runners\":[5,6,7,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
